WEBVTT

NOTE
Captions for the WORQsense launch video.
Speakers: Sreevidya Varma (Principal), Daren Jay (IMS), Kavita Khanna (Co-founder)
Timestamps are estimates — adjust against the actual video if needed.

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.500
India's workplace dispute resolution obligations
are maturing and expanding.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:16.000
Sexual harassment prevention law, industrial relations code —
they are all setting a new standard for scrutiny.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.500
Compliance is the baseline.
Capability is the differentiator.

00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:29.000
I'm Sreevidya Varma, a workplace investigator with a decade
resolving high-stake cases for India's largest corporates.

00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:37.500
This is WORQsense, designed to build capability in internal investigations
and the system rebuild that follows.

00:00:37.500 --> 00:00:47.000
Because today organisations need more than having policies
and conducting trainings that teach them the act.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:55.000
They need skill in gathering evidence, understanding systems,
and conducting inquiries that hold.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:01.000
That's the skill WORQsense helps you build.

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:11.000
Hello, I'm Daren Jay, CEO of Interview Management Solutions
and creator of the TILES System®.

00:01:11.000 --> 00:01:20.000
I've taught investigative interviewing around the world for over 30 years,
including at the Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel National Police Academy in Hyderabad.

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:26.000
And I'm genuinely delighted to be partnering with WORQsense
as their global training partner.

00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:36.000
The WORQsense team have deep expertise in the prevention of sexual harassment,
the workings of internal committees,

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:44.000
and they've conducted a wide range of workplace investigations
across India and New Zealand,

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:51.000
and they have an understanding of the realities Internal Committee
and HR teams actually face.

00:01:51.000 --> 00:02:00.000
My role is to bring advanced evidence-based interviewing training
and the TILES System technology to complement that expertise.

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:10.000
Together, we're combining the PEACE model and the Mendez Principles with software
that makes strategic interviewing skills observable, measurable, and defensible.

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:15.500
I'm really proud to be working alongside the WORQsense team.

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:24.000
Every incident reveals something about the system
that enabled it to happen.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:33.000
Addressing the incident is important, but what is more important
is understanding the system that enabled it to happen.

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:38.500
Hi, I'm Kavita Khanna, the co-founder of WORQsense.

00:02:38.500 --> 00:02:46.000
I have over 25 years of leadership experience
in businesses of different scale and maturity.

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:55.000
I built ReWireWorks, a diagnostic tool that helps leaders identify
the system conditions that led to high-risk incidents.

00:02:55.000 --> 00:03:03.000
The diagnostic grew from the questions that helped me create clarity
in real organisation settings —

00:03:03.000 --> 00:03:09.000
questions about how decisions moved,
where trust held or broke.

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:18.000
ReWireWorks shows you exactly where your system needs strengthening
and what you already have to work with.

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:29.000
What I know through my experience is that most organisations are working
much harder than they need to, because they're fixing symptoms
instead of understanding the system.

00:03:31.000 --> 00:03:36.000
WORQsense brings it together.

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:43.000
Investigation capability, evidence-based interviewing standards,
and systems intelligence.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:48.000
Built for your teams across India and New Zealand.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:57.000
If your internal investigation teams aren't equipped to run
what they are required to run, give us a shout.

00:03:57.000 --> 00:04:01.000
Visit worqsense.com.
